Who we are
Welcome to Fore Indoor Golf Club, the original indoor golf facility in Highlands County, FL. Owned and operated by William M. Carroll, the club was born out of a simple yet powerful desire to make golf accessible year-round, regardless of the weather. Whether it's a rainy day, scorching heat, or abnormal cold, we provide the perfect environment to enjoy the game you love in any season.
At Fore Indoor Golf Club, we offer a state-of-the-art indoor golfing experience designed for players of all levels, ages, and/or gender. Our goal is to create a welcoming space where golfers can practice, play, and connect with others, all while enjoying the comfort and convenience of our climate-controlled setting.
Join us and experience golf like never before—rain or shine, day or night!
